column5: I'm catching up.. out fished her yesterday.. Im only down by two now!!!
You might do better if'n you was to wear a proper fishing hat....
Good morning.  Nice shots TJ.  Maybe one day you will be as good as her.
I can out fish the WIFE also,When I leave her at home.
Want me to send you a hat, TJ? Wow, throw a Thill in that water and the ripples would reach both sides. Glad you're having a good time.
I'm betting he'll have to Google "Thill."
love that beaver picture!  looks like your having a great time!
Awesome TJ! Man I miss northern Ontario fishing.
